Subject: Request for Password Reset and Assistance
Description:
Dear Team,

The UI console password has expired, and we have since reset it to a new password. However, we are currently unable to log in using the new password. We kindly request your assistance in resetting the password on the server.

Could you please schedule a call today based on your availability to help resolve the issue?

Solution_Comment__c: removed shadows and setup audit log backup.
